uch\nthat the precursor to the Laughlin state could be realized in current ultracold\natom, Josephson junction array, and quantum circuit experiments.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 15 Dec 2016 16:45:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 20 Feb 2017 23:28:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-08-16"}
