 existence in proto-solar clouds needs to be\nexplored, given that the stellar lifetimes are longer than the molecular cloud\nlifetimes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 15 Dec 2016 23:43:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-02-22"}
